name: ENHYPEN
description: ENHYPEN is a 4th generation boy group formed through I-LAND, known for their vampire concepts, powerful choreography, and global popularity.

funFacts: Youngest leader in HYBE family
Known for his cat-like visuals and dimples
His name 'Jungwon' means garden in Korean
Finished 3rd place on I-LAND
Despite being leader, he's the second youngest
members.bio: Jungwon is ENHYPEN's leader despite being one of the youngest members. His cat-like visuals, dimples, and mature leadership have earned him respect. He became one of the youngest leaders in K-Pop history at just 16.

funFacts: Trained at Big Hit for 3 years before I-LAND
Known as the 'ace' for his all-rounder abilities
Finished 1st place on I-LAND
Has deer-like visuals and long limbs
Was friends with TXT members during training
members.bio: Heeseung is ENHYPEN's eldest member and ace, excelling at vocals, dance, and rap. His 3 years of Big Hit training made him a standout on I-LAND where he finished first. His deer-like visuals and all-rounder talents make him irreplaceable.

funFacts: Lived in USA until age 9
Known for his exceptional fashion sense
A talented cook, often makes food for members
Fluent in English and Korean
His fierce stage presence contrasts his caring personality
members.bio: Jay is ENHYPEN's fashion icon and lead rapper. Having lived in the USA, he's fluent in English and brings international appeal. His fierce stage presence and cooking skills for members show his caring, multifaceted personality.

funFacts: Born in Korea, raised in Australia
Has a dog named Layla he loves dearly
Known for his puppy-like personality
Only trained for 9 months before I-LAND
His Australian accent is adored by fans
members.bio: Jake is ENHYPEN's Australian member known for his puppy-like charm. Despite having only 9 months of training, his natural talent shone through. His warm personality and love for his dog Layla have made him beloved worldwide.

funFacts: Was a competitive figure skater before becoming an idol
Won numerous skating competitions nationally
Known for his ice prince visuals
Quiet and introverted but opens up on stage
His grace from skating shows in his dancing
members.bio: Sunghoon is ENHYPEN's visual and former figure skater. He competed nationally before choosing the idol path. His elegant skating background gives him unique grace on stage, and his 'ice prince' visuals are stunning.

funFacts: Known for his bright, sunshine personality
Best friends with TXT's Taehyun and Stray Kids' Hyunjin
His aegyo is legendary in ENHYPEN
Entered I-LAND through global auditions
Always makes members and fans smile
members.bio: Sunoo is ENHYPEN's sunshine and mood maker. His bright personality and adorable aegyo light up every room. Despite initial doubts during I-LAND, his charm won producers and fans over, securing his spot in the final lineup.

funFacts: From Okayama, Japan
Was a backup dancer for SHINee as a child
Known as a dance prodigy since young age
Youngest ENHYPEN member but very charismatic
His growth spurt made him one of the tallest
members.bio: Ni-ki is ENHYPEN's Japanese maknae and main dancer, known as a dance prodigy. He danced for SHINee as a child and has been training since young. Despite being the youngest, his dance skills rival professionals.
